entry.value: In review at Notebookcheck is the Asus ExpertBook B6 Flip. Even for a workstation with a 16-inch screen, it is quite large and heavy. On the other hand, it houses an efficient cooling system inside that easily copes with 140 watts of waste heat from the Intel Core i9-12950HX and Nvidia RTX A2000.
